definition: Bulgaria/Bulgarian/abbr. for 保加利亞|保加利亚[Bao3 jia1 li4 ya4]
to defend/to protect/to keep/to guarantee/to ensure/civil administration unit in the baojia 保甲[bao3 jia3] system (old)
thick pole/bar/rod/thick line/to mark with a thick line/to sharpen (knife)/(old) coffin-bearing pole

sentences.english: See the picture, this PT Cruiser has chrome front bumper and hubcaps.
sentences.chinese: 這輛車的前保險槓和輪蓋都是電鍍的。

sentences.english: The fenders had fallen off that old bus.
sentences.chinese: 保險槓已從那輛破舊的汽車上脫落下來。

sentences.english: Lamp, Bumper, Mirror, Hood, Fender, Frame of water tank.
sentences.chinese: 大燈，保險槓，倒車鏡，機蓋，葉子板，水箱框架。

sentences.english: Remove 2 Philips screws on each side of the bumper in wheel wells.
sentences.chinese: 刪除2飛利浦螺絲釘，每邊的保險槓在車輪水井。

sentences.english: The Zenki front bumper was replaced by a smoother, more modern-looking front bumper cover.
sentences.chinese: 其前保險槓變得更加圓潤更具現代感。

sentences.english: Yet, we have taken that phrase, and we have made bumper stickers out of it and t-shirts and everything else.
sentences.chinese: 我們把它製作成汽車保險槓貼紙，T恤衫和其他東西。

sentences.english: Larger air intakes and odd - shaped fog lights are built into the front bumper.
sentences.chinese: 更大的進氣口和奇形霧燈，內置的前保險槓。

sentences.english: Flat-fronted chassis with twin mini- bumpers for impact-damage resistance.
sentences.chinese: 平板門前底盤與孿生小保險槓影響損傷的阻力。

sentences.english: The bumper sticker, if you want peace work for justice,that's where James is.
sentences.chinese: 汽車保險槓貼紙，雅各的觀點是讓和平爲公正效力。

sentences.english: Can you straighten out the dent in the bumper?
sentences.chinese: 你能將保險槓上的凹處修理好嗎？

sentences.english: Tin cans are often tied to the bumper.
sentences.chinese: 保險槓上常吊着一些錫質的罐頭瓶。

sentences.english: Our bumpers just grazed (ie touched each other)as we passed.
sentences.chinese: 我們錯車時保險槓互相蹭了一下。

sentences.english: The crashworthiness of truck bumper in a low velocity crash was discussed.
sentences.chinese: 針對某重型載重汽車保險槓開展低速碰撞安全性研究。

sentences.english: So he backed Benny up and hitched Benny to the man's car bumper.
sentences.chinese: 於是農夫讓班尼後退，並把它拴到車的保險槓上。

sentences.english: A vehicle two-body bumper belongs to a vehicle component.
sentences.chinese: 汽車兩體保險槓屬於汽車部件。

sentences.english: Bumpers play a very important role during a low-velocity crash.
sentences.chinese: 在低速碰撞過程中，保險槓發揮了舉足輕重的地位。
